            <section class="reason">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="reason-wrapper">
                        <img src="/website_dt/static/src/images/up-quote.svg" class="reason-image"/>
                        <div class="reason-content">
                            <h2 class="reason-heading">Why do people buy DataTile? When they try to process their survey results in popular BI tools, they fail, and then they turn to DataTile for the solution that works.
